OL,3,CShoplifter who was banned from every
OL,4,CB&M store in the UK has been jailed
OL,6,FA 'prolific' shoplifter from
OL,7,FLancashire who was banned from every
OL,8,FB&M store in the UK has been jailed.
OL,10,FStuart Astley was handed a Criminal
OL,11,FBehaviour Order (CBO) last month
OL,12,Fpreventing him from entering Tawd
OL,13,FValley Retail Park in Skelmersdale and
OL,14,Fany B&M store in the country.
OL,16,FHe was later charged with three counts
OL,17,Fof theft from a shop and four counts
OL,18,Fof breaching the CBO.
