OL,3,CShoplifter who was banned from every
OL,4,CB&M store in the UK has been jailed
OL,6,FAstley, of Caister Close,
OL,7,FSkelmersdale, appeared at Preston
OL,8,FMagistrates Court on Monday where he
OL,9,Fpleaded guilty to the offences and was
OL,10,Fsentenced to four months in prison.
OL,12,FPC Rebecca Birchall from West
OL,13,FLancashire's Neighbourhood Policing
OL,14,Fteam said: "Retail crime can have a
OL,15,Fsignificant negative impact on
OL,16,Fbusinesses, shop staff and our local
OL,17,Fcommunities and this action shows just
OL,18,Fhow seriously we are tackling it.
