OL,6,F"We will continue to closely monitor
OL,7,Fthose who have been issued Criminal
OL,8,FBehaviour Orders and act quickly if
OL,9,Fthey continue offending in our shops
OL,10,Fso that it feels safe and secure for
OL,11,Fall those to live, work in and visit
OL,12,FWest Lancashire."
OL,14,FA force spokesperson added: "Operation
OL,15,FVulture is Lancashire Constabulary's
OL,16,Fresponse to shoplifting across the
OL,17,Fcounty, backed by Lancashire's Police
OL,18,Fand Crime Commissioner Clive Grunshaw.
